# The `MemDGNode` Class Reference

<DoxygenPage pluginConfig={pluginConfig}>

A <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/sandboxir/dependencygraph">DependencyGraph</a> <a href="/docs/api/classes/node">Node</a> for instructions that may read/write memory, or have some ordering constraints, like with stacksave/stackrestore and alloca/inalloca. <a href="#details">More...</a>

## Description {#details}

A <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/sandboxir/dependencygraph">DependencyGraph</a> <a href="/docs/api/classes/node">Node</a> for instructions that may read/write memory, or have some ordering constraints, like with stacksave/stackrestore and alloca/inalloca.
